        <p class="text-[1.05rem] leading-[1.8] text-[#666]">
          After the glory years of the 1960s, things went downhill, with the club spending time in both Denmark's second and third tier. From 1974 to 1985, AB's first team was consistently placed in the country's second tier, despite countless chances of promotion. In the 1986 season, the club was relegated to the 3rd division, and for one year came close to dropping into the Danish amateur league altogether.
        </p>
