              </div>
            ))
          }
        </div>

        <p class="text-[1.1rem] leading-[1.75] text-[#444] mt-8">
          These three greats helped AB return to the country's top league in 1996, where they won bronze medals in 1999 and 2000, as well as a cup triumph in 1999 with a 2-1 win over AaB.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[1.1rem] leading-[1.75] text-[#444] mt-5">
