          <p class="text-[1.1rem] leading-[1.75] text-[#111]">
            After 8 seasons in the country's top league, AB left the Superliga in 2004 and were relegated to the 1st Division. AB began to rebuild, targeting promotion in 2010 — rallying supporters and players around the call to action:
          </p>
          <div class="border-l-[3px] border-ab-green pl-6 my-6">
