          <p class="text-[1.1rem] leading-[1.75] text-[#444] mt-5">
            AB hired head coach David Roufpanah for the 2023-2024 season, who brought extensive coaching experience from Allsvenskan, Superettan, the Swedish 2nd division and Damallsvenskan. AB finished that season with 9 wins, 13 draws and 10 losses.
