          <p class="text-[1.15rem] leading-[1.75] text-white/85">
            In April 2025, Green Owls Football Holdings ("Green Owls") became a minority shareholder. The investment supported the club's mission by strengthening the squad, enhancing the fan experience, expanding sponsor partnerships and deepening community outreach, while leveraging technological and infrastructural upgrades to optimise the club.
          </p>
          <p class="text-[1.15rem] leading-[1.75] text-white/85 mt-5">
